<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Statistical ensemble (mathematical physics)</h1>			<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
				<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>				<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">  (Redirected from <a href="/w/index.php?title=Statistical_ensemble&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Statistical ensemble">Statistical ensemble</a>)</span></div>
